      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and is super comfy for those long drives or just zipping around town. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
