    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing inspection. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight factory tolerances, making this a mechanically sound performer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
