    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Finished in a timeless exterior that still retains a deep gloss, it has been kept in a climate-controlled garage when not in use. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; the engine delivers power smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. We have a complete service history showing regular maintenance and recent fluid flushes. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space with leather upholstery that is supple and free of tears, showing only very light, age-appropriate creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronics, including the premium sound system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. While you may find a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel, these are purely cosmetic and do not detract from the car's overall impressive road presence. This is a reliable, well-cared-for machine ready for its next owner to enjoy without delay.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
