    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it drives like a dream! Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
