      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen features crisp VANOS actuation and retains its factory-rated linear power delivery through the individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox is paired with a firm clutch, sending power to a functional limited-slip differential. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The suspension geometry remains tight with updated bushings, providing the communicative feedback typical of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is optimized for performance-oriented driving.",
